Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reasons and hints are all connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With these, the truth unravels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The love was misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's case makes everything clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okino Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} invited us to a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:46.00,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Okino Yoko (22)\NIdol
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was a member of the idol group, the Earth Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.67,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Kaoru Kusano (20)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It turned out to be Kusano Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s engagement party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other members of the Earth Ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.30,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Yuki Takeno (22)\NMulti-talented
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takeno Yuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:03.10,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Hoshino Terumi (23)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Hoshino Terumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} also showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, when Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was taking a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she was attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:20.78,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Idol Stars' Secret\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be searching for the most important thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dagger that slashed Kaoru's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you find it in this apartment or among our possessions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the murderer is one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think an outsider would leave the\Nmurder weapon inside the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it was wiped clean, there would still be traces\Nof blood that forensics would find with luminol.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not something that one can easily hide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure do know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm into mysteries these days, because of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Takagi, you search Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} while\Nthe policewomen search the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest of you, carefully search for the murder weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Inspector, if the culprit is Makuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, then\Nhe could've disposed of the weapon by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked the people in the ambulance to call\Nme if he tried to do anything strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takeno{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, if you don't mind stepping in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wasn't Yuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a regular on\Nthe show "Detective Samonji"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she was the annoying journalist\Nwho kept following Samonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, when she sent in her resignation\Nin order to take care of her sick father,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she was replaced by Kaoru, although\NTerumi was their first choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Terumi would've gotten the role if it hadn't been for\NMakuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s begging. That's why Kaoru got the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} described Makuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as a depressing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wanted to be a star as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in the same studio as us, but he\Ngave up and became Kaoru's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even though Kaoru speaks about him like that, the\Ntruth is that she cares a lot about Makuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always said that he lacked resolve,\Nand that he gave up too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you weren't able to find the murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's neither in this apartment, nor in any drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you also check their accessories?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s fake nails, Terumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s earrings,\Nand even Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they all turned up negative on the luminol test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what about Makuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that they even tested his\Nglasses, but they found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And until the detectives arrived, he was\Nsitting in a chair with his head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then was the murder weapon really\Ntaken outside by the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems likely that the criminal came\Nfrom outside the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they didn't know that Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then suddenly walking into the apartment and\Ncommitting the murder is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if the murderer is someone from inside, then\Nthe murder weapon must be somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't we find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found a listening device in this doll.\NIt must be from one of her fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It also seems that her drawers have been tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means that if someone had been spying on Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would have known about her engagement\Nand her location in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if the person was one of her biggest fans, he could have\Nattacked her and taken something as a gift for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contact her studio immediately and ask them if there are\Nany dangerous fans out there that we should be aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These must be the drawers that man was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drawers containing pens and scissors are messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones containing makeup and jewelry\Nhaven't even been touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be invading someone's privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Women have things that they don't\Nwant others to know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For that reason, they do some stupid things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That picture, please put it back where you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's no longer there, Kaoru could get extremely upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it. I know what weapon the murderer used!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how they got rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the murder weapon isn't in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means this was an outside job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a chance it was one of her angry fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, all we can do is hope that she recovers\Nfast in order to help solve this mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She might have seen the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Kaoru's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened? It's the hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that Kaoru is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The surgery went fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll wake up in a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you should be there when Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwakes up, since you're her fiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But are you sure that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hospital is swamped with reporters\Nwho have heard about the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could always go later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna annoy the patients or mislead the reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mislead them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to tell everyone the truth\Nabout the engagement party now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your plan didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one that did it, right? The criminal\Nthat drugged Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and slit her throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you're smart enough to be a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you can't find the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tool that was used to cut her\Nthroat is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I certainly don't have a knife on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm really the criminal, then can you tell\Nme where I hid the murder weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know where it is, but I know what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a sharp tool stuck on your finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean these fake nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the police have already checked them, andâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Those nails are for camouflage only.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is that the weapon is hidden\Nunderneath those fake nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next hardest thing in the human body after the\Nteeth, and a weapon only a woman could use:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's her real, edge-sharp nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My guess is that you used your strong right thumb nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before using it, you covered it up with a fake nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, you clipped your nail\Nuntil it reached normal size.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, you covered it up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would notice that the real\Nnail was as long as the fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you used old gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You put a hole in them so that the nail could pass through.\NYou even used a raincoat to avoid the splattered blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, you intentionally threw the coat and gloves\Noutside so it would appear that the culprit ran outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Effectively making it seem like the\Ncrime was committed by a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even sent the letters and the doll to Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Yuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the murder weapon was a real nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's true, then there must be a nail clipper\Nwith traces of Kaoru's blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your plan was to find one of Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You needed it to hide the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you weren't able to find one among her stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} uses a nail file instead of a nail clipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was me, I'd use scissors to cut my nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You would never use scissors because the police would\Ncheck them as a potential murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If blood was found on them, this case would easily be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nail clipper would never be tested because\Nit can't be used to cut someone's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't bring your own nail clipper\Nwith you, it would be too suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew that all of the suspects' belongings\Nwould be checked, including yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you said yourself that I couldn't have used a nail clipper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you think I cut my nail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I just tell you? There is something stronger\Nthan the nails in the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:13:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You clipped your nails by biting them,\Nthen threw them down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, it wouldn't look threatening enough to be\Nconsidered a weapon, and would be overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I have proof that you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, look at your kiss mark on this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't very obvious, but you can see where it's darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood on your lips,\Nleft from when you bit off your nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even without your deduction, Kaoru\Ncould've told you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called her from outside the bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and drugged her when she came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could she have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could she have taken something before I followed her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I fell in love with Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} the\Nfirst day we performed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Kaoru stole him {\i1}and{\i0} my role from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I congratulated her, you know what she told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all made up. It's just a rumor started by the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was shocked, but before I knew what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was engulfed in a frenzy of jealousy\Nthat I never felt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the reason Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kaoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} never got engaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could have killed her if I had cut deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw her face, I just froze... I knew I couldn't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm t-truly glad that... that she didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What did she take?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her face is pale and blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her hand is shaking and her pulse is rapid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, she just fainted...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father is in the hospital for diabetes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, it could be... the diabetes medication!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:36.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Blood Sugar Medication
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Diabetics are usually prescribed a\Nmedicine that lowers blood sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can be deadly if it's abused.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a normal person took the drug, their\Nblood sugar would drop drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I leave her like this, she'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must have prepared it ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit, I won't let her die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not because of this senseless delusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let her die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haido Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were unconscious for two whole days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you mistake your father's\Nmedicine for your vitamins?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go tell Terumi that you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaoru, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I told the police everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told them that someone attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told them it was an old fat lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, I told them it was an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want them thinking that some\Npsycho stalker was after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I should thank you for giving me this wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my punishment for lying for so long\Nwithout considering your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the engagement party was fake.\NI asked Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was trying to make a certain someone jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to marry in my 20s, just like Kudo Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, my dream has come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's front page now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He finally proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:19:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You still like that weakling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know he seems like a chicken, but he's a marvelous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should hear what he said in front of the reporters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose that someone that I treasure the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, a lot has happened today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But thanks to Terumi, the plan was\Nable to work out pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Terumi was in on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We never actually had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the Earth Ladies were still together, Terumi\Nused to visit me and give me a lot of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We made up that fight as the reason our group was\Nbreaking up. Sorry we never told you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. You made up the fight so it would\Nbe easier for us to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what was the "Sorry to hear about it" on the card for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that boy said she probably meant that\Nshe was sorry the plan didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Apparently, Detective\NMouri has trained him well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He saw Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} trying to cover me up with\Na towel before getting me out of the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how he knew we weren't really engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He saw a picture of me with Makuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, but\NTerumi's attitude is what made him suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, he kept asking me questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one who fed you all that sugar when\Nhe saw you passed out on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what about Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? Hurry up and tell him\Nhow you feel before Terumi beats you to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:58.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said Terumi likes mysteries, and that she\Nmust like the man who plays Detective Samonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, he's mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kenzaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} told Terumi how he feels about\Nher but was completely ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then who's the person that she likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows, but she usually likes younger guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:22:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scene 7, Terumi forces her opponent to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, you have to act like a cool, heartless woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made a fatal mistake that will bring about your defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:30.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Your pieces look as though they have\Na strong formation, but they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's more of a detective than a Shogi player.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The move you made with your bishop was your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
